              "content": "Analyze game review data to identify critical business risks and actionable fixes.\n\n**Input:** List of reviews with description, sentiment, and category\n\n**Output:** Business intelligence summary prioritized by impact:\n\n**CRITICAL RISKS** (Major threats to retention/revenue)\n- **[Issue]** - [Business impact and player volume affected]\n- Fix Priority: [High/Medium] \n- Estimated Impact: [Player churn risk/revenue loss]\n\n**OPERATIONAL FIXES** (Addressable technical/design issues)\n- **[Issue]** - [Specific fix needed and expected outcome]\n- Development Effort: [Low/Medium/High]\n- Player Satisfaction Gain: [Estimated improvement]\n\n**Requirements:**\n- Prioritize by business risk (player churn, negative review velocity, revenue impact)\n- Include affected player volume/percentage for each issue\n- Focus on fixable problems with clear solutions\n- Distinguish between quick wins vs major development efforts\n- Use data-driven language, avoid subjective descriptions\n\n**Input:** List of reviews with description, sentiment, and category (e.g., performance, story, gameplay)\n\n**Output:** Structured summary with:\n- Category name\n- Key weakness description (1-2 sentences)\n- Player impact score (1-5, where 5 = severely affects gameplay)\n\n**Format:**\n**[Category]** - [Weakness summary]\nImpact: [Score]/5\n\n**Requirements:**\n- Focus only on significant negative patterns\n- Prioritize issues mentioned across multiple reviews\n- Use clear, actionable language",
